		<td><b> Megx.net allows access to integrated environmental and
		(meta)genomic data intended for use in marine microbial ecology</b>
		</p>
		<p
			style="font-family: Arial; font-style: italic; font-weight: bold; font-size: 15px; color: cornflowerblue"
